title: Le'Veon Bell Interview, MVP Race, Brady Hurt? (Football 12/13)
description:
Will Brinson, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora bring you this midweek edition of the Pick Six podcast with a heavy focus on Tom Brady and his poor performance vs. the Dolphins on Monday Night Football. The guys also discuss the AFC playoff picture and Pete's hot take that the Jags might be the best team in the conference. Then, strap in for a heated MVP debate, not just about who should win, but about the meaning of the award. Nick Kostos joins on the phone to interview Steelers RB Le'Veon Bell.
